Properties Where People
Like to Work, Shop, and Live

The way we live, work, and interact is constantly evolving. Todays and tomorrows markets demand innovative solutions that transcend conventional boundaries and offer unique experiences. This is where Ashtrom Properties excels, providing adaptable solutions that meet changing tenant needs, while maintaining a strong focus on exceptional customer service.

Work Where You Enjoy,
Enjoy Where You Work

Imagine starting your workday with a gym session, then savoring a coffee break in the rooftop garden, dining at our diverse culinary complex, and even doing some shopping at our on-site stores before heading home. Ashtrom Properties is redesigning our work environment to seamlessly integrate work and personal life, optimizing time management in a dynamic setting.

Our Office Buildings
Our Office Buildings

Ashtrom Port: Helping You Grow

Ashtrom Port is a meticulously managed office complex designed to meet the evolving needs of expanding businesses. With comprehensive management services and top-tier amenities, Ashtrom Port provides a unique experience for both employees and clients, allowing you to focus on achieving success.

More on Ashtrom Port
More on Ashtrom Port

Ashtrom Host: Enhancing Tenant Experience

Introducing Ashtrom Host, an innovative app designed to transform the tenant experience in our office buildings. With Ashtrom Host, tenants can easily manage parking access, identify guests, report issues, reserve meeting rooms, and even book lunch reservations in the culinary complex. In short, Ashtrom Host makes life more convenient and comfortable for everyone involved.

Eco-Friendly Properties

At Ashtrom Properties, sustainability is central to everything we do. As part of our corporate responsibility, we design eco-friendly buildings that meet LEED GOLD standards. Our projects feature green spaces, easy access to public transportation, solar panels on select roofs, and energy-efficient solutions. Additionally, we ensure physical and digital accessibility across all of assets, creating a safe and healthy environment for both employees and tenants.

ESG Report

Mixed-Use Properties:
All in One Place

In recent years, Ashtrom Properties has embraced the global trend in urban planning by launching mixed-use projects. Our vision is to create a comfortable, high-quality, and ecological living environment where people can live, work, shop, and socializeall within one complex that operates 24/7.
